## Technical Notes
- **PDF form field names**: date, mlo name, lo_title, lo_nmls, lo_phone, lo_email, client, property_address, offer_price, ltv, max ltv, max_loan_amount, loan_type, fico, Text11 (signature), additional_notes, doc_0-5 (checkboxes), Dropdown3/44/55/66 (doc type dropdowns)
- **Tax data structure**: TAX_DATA.states[stateCode].rate = state avg %, .counties[].rate = county %
- **MONARCH brand**: #F4F5EE bg, #0D3B66 navy, #C9A84C gold, Inter font
